definitions.definition: Not able to be located ; gone , misplaced .
Not present when it (they) should be.
examples: Joe went missing last year. He had all teeth missing when he was finally found.
We've got some flatware missing - There seem to be some cooking utensils missing too!

definitions.definition: Of an internal combustion engine : running roughly due to an occasional lack of a spark or other irregular fault .
